[normal]Our starting-point is that t
[normal]he BBC exists to have a positive impact on society by bringing the best 
[normal]in 
[normal]media content to 
[normal]everyone. Our mission is to 
[normal]inform, educate and entertain; provide 
[normal]value to all audiences not just some; introduce audiences to things they love but otherwise might not have discovered; and focus on the quality and depth of impact, not just the quantity of consumption. While the primary purpose of the BBC is to serve audi
[normal]ences and society, 
