[normal]3) What scope, [bold]scale and remit[bold] should the BBC have?[bold] [bold]Should the BBC’s output and services be provided to any greater or lesser degree for particular audiences? [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]30.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]The
[normal] BBC
[normal]’s remit
[normal] 
[normal]requires us to provide something of value for everyone and 
[normal]to 
[normal]provide
[normal] a wide range of programme
[normal]s
[normal] and services
[normal] in order to do so
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]Au
[normal]diences 
[normal]support this 
[normal]remit
